{"data": [{"id": "4741526", "title": "BuzzFeed: This Rally Can Last Longer", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"BuzzFeed office in NYC\" data-id=\"1036116888\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3817px\" height=\"2736px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Roman Tiraspolsky</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Summary</h2> <p>After a disastrous SPAC merger in 2021, <b>BuzzFeed, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BZFD\" title=\"BuzzFeed, Inc.\">BZFD</a></span>) has quietly surged over 300% in 2024. The company's strategic shift to use AI tools in its workflow to generate quizzes, articles, and other digital content has positioned them</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741526-buzzfeed-this-rally-can-last-longer", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 20:07:53"}, {"id": "4741539", "title": "Navigating Troubled Waters: What The Surge In Bankruptcy Filings Means For The Economy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Piggy bank in pieces\" data-id=\"1222778351\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5086px\" height=\"3509px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The financial landscape is showing signs of strain as bankruptcy filings surge, with businesses and consumers alike feeling the pressure of shifting economic conditions. Despite Federal Reserve rate cuts aimed at stabilizing the market, historical patterns suggest that monetary policy</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741539-navigating-troubled-waters-what-the-surge-in-bankruptcy-filings-means-for-the-economy", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 20:04:00"}, {"id": "4741524", "title": "Medtronic: Guidance Raised, Solid Dividend, Shares Still A Bargain", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Medtronic office in Silicon Valley, Santa Clara, California, USA\" data-id=\"1689196299\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Health Care sector has taken it on the chin in the past month. President-elect Trump's win, and subsequent pick to lead the Department of Health and Human Services (HHS), was met with selling pressure in November across much of the pharma and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741524-medtronic-guidance-raised-solid-dividend-shares-still-a-bargain", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 20:02:00"}, {"id": "4741522", "title": "Avoid Universal Corp. Stock: Looking Beyond The Recent NYSE Non-Compliance Notice", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165947546/image_165947546.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Tobacco Crop\" data-id=\"165947546\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165947546/image_165947546.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165947546/image_165947546.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165947546/image_165947546.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165947546/image_165947546.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165947546/image_165947546.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165947546/image_165947546.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165947546/image_165947546.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165947546/