.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436566821/image_1436566821.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436566821/image_1436566821.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436566821/image_1436566821.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436566821/image_1436566821.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">fongfong2</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>A lot more difficult. </p> <p>That's what the global economic environment has become. </p> <p>As most of you may know, most of my research is based on the \"big picture,\" which includes interrelated factors like macroeconomics, geopolitics, and supply chains. Right now, all of these are extremely volatile. </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436566821/image_1436566821.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741520-mission-critical-cameco-goes-nuclear", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 19:43:23"}, {"id": "4741518", "title": "Sealed Air: On The Sidelines Until Recovery Becomes Clear", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1349030861/image_1349030861.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close-up of a female warehouse worker sealing the box on a conveyor belt\" data-id=\"1349030861\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1349030861/image_1349030861.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1349030861/image_1349030861.jpg?io=