ss board behind business man background. Business concept to present financial information and marketing strategy analysis. Investment target in global economy and digital commercial.\" data-id=\"1304022517\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">phongphan5922/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p>The Eaton Vance Senior Income Trust (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EVF\" title=\"Eaton Vance Senior Income Trust\">EVF</a></span>) is a leveraged loan closed end fund. The name comes from the Eaton Vance fund family, and has a relatively modest AUM of only $110 million. The CEF has posted</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741517-evf-lacks-appeal-in-todays-environment", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 19:36:04"}, {"id": "4741474", "title": "Petrobras: There's Still Time To Buy This On The Cheap", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351375648/image_1351375648.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Architecture in Rio downtown\" data-id=\"1351375648\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351375648/image_1351375648.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351375648/image_1351375648.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351375648/image_1351375648.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351375648/image_1351375648.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351375648/image_1351375648.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351375648/image_1351375648.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351375648/image_1351375648.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351375648/image_1351375648.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">FerreiraSilva</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Petr\u00f3leo Brasileiro S.A. - Petrobras (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PBR\" title=\"Petr\u00f3leo Brasileiro S.A. - Pet